{"tid":1893623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上皇出事 明仁有疑似肺炎症狀 缺席天皇生日會","createTime":"2020-02-23T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T11:48:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b17e2f03292d360ed308a640341265f3f863e49a","tid":1893623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"堅中嘅話，安倍今次切腹都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bdabc3223e4d1bc953a45f2af065d1fc5df406","tid":1893623,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"7a6315fb6a95080fb8be415893485cba4929608a","tid":1893623,"uid":186997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"【速報】上皇さま 風邪の症状で&ldquo;あいさつ&rdquo;見送り<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fnn.jp/posts/00432659CX/202002231815_CX_CX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fnn.jp%2Fposts%2F00432659CX%2F202002231815_CX_CX&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=2a8adcad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fnn.jp/posts/00432659CX/202002231815_CX_CX</a>"},{"pid":"423f2c607323d677cfae795674eb355987ff7226","tid":1893623,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b17e2f03292d360ed308a640341265f3f863e49a","tid":1893623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"堅中嘅話，安倍今次切腹都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"佢都唔係第一次肺炎架啦"},{"pid":"8cbfe422a207ecb6cf3becb29d0075fe11faaf1e","tid":1893623,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:40:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日本天皇：期待即將到來的東京奧運會 擔心疫情傳播</span><br />\n2020年02月23日 08:36:44  編輯：Nicole_86<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://oss.suning.com/snsis/channel_content/iebg2mKNGilyja8GDNbh-ympdCVQ8ljyf03Bks194YmlZaMm2G3j5dryhP7Iu-Zt.jpg?imgW=1082&amp;imgH=594\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foss.suning.com%2Fsnsis%2Fchannel_content%2Fiebg2mKNGilyja8GDNbh-ympdCVQ8ljyf03Bks194YmlZaMm2G3j5dryhP7Iu-Zt.jpg%3FimgW%3D1082%26imgH%3D594&h=324525ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月23日消息，日本德仁天皇表示，他期待著即將到來的東京奧運會，與此同時他也擔心新型冠狀病毒的傳播會對奧運會造成影響，目前新冠病毒已經在日本造成3人死亡，並在全國範圍內緩慢蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n周日迎來60歲生日的德仁天皇於去年5月登基，他的父親明仁天皇成為兩個世紀以來首位退位的日本天皇。德仁天皇在22日的於東京舉辦的生日新聞發佈會上表示，目前，日本各地有80多人被確診，為阻止疫情蔓延，全國各地都取消了相關活動。<br />\n<br />\n日本也取消本月23日舉行的天皇誕生日典禮。日本德仁天皇出生于1960年2月23日，他去年繼位之後，每年的2月23將是天皇誕生日。依照慣例會舉行生日典禮。今年是首次，由於新型冠狀病毒的流行，因故取消。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這種新型冠狀病毒令人擔憂。我想對那些被感染的人和他們的家人表示同情。&rdquo;德仁天皇在精簡的生日發佈會上發表演講，&ldquo;與此同時，為防止感染的蔓延。我希望醫護人員的努力很快會有結果。&rdquo;<br />\n東京將於7月24日第二次舉辦夏季奧運會。德仁說，1964年，在他四歲時舉辦的第一屆東京奧運會是他童年的一個精彩時刻。<br />\n<br />\n在第二次世界大戰慘敗、東京成為一片廢墟不到20年後舉行的這屆奧運會，在日本被視為標誌著日本重返國際社會。德仁和他的父母一起觀看了馬拉松、馬術比賽和閉幕式，然後是皇太子和公主。他說:&ldquo;在閉幕式上，運動員們並沒有代表各自國家的代表隊入場，而是以一種非常愉快的心情一起入場。這令他感到印象深刻&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ppsport.com/article/news/849684.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ppsport.com%2Farticle%2Fnews%2F849684.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=379ee629\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ppsport.com/article/news/849684.html</a>"},{"pid":"577f42ad95519419c6356a4557b944d4f4b72c0c","tid":1893623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"423f2c607323d677cfae795674eb355987ff7226","tid":1893623,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b17e2f03292d360ed308a640341265f3f863e49a","tid":1893623,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"堅中嘅話，安倍今次切腹都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"佢都唔係第一次肺炎架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:43:57.000Z","msg":"萬一支那肺炎中左點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人實大吹大擂話支那肺炎為國增光，討死日皇為支那人報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacd58af03bbbece2b627b2fed746dd2be6ed978","tid":1893623,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"上乜鳩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />風邪"}]}